'''球盖菇科'''（[[學名|學名]]：Strophariaceae）是[[担子菌门|担子菌门]][[伞菌目|伞菌目]]的一個[[科_(生物)|科]]，於1946年由[[洛夫·辛格|洛夫·辛格]]與{{link-en|亞歷山大·H·史密斯|Alexander H. Smith}}定義<ref name="Singer 1946">{{cite journal |vauthors=Singer R, Smith AH |title=The taxonomic position of ''Pholiota mutabilis'' and related species |journal=Mycologia |year=1946 |volume=38 |issue=5 |pages=500–523 |url=http://www.cybertruffle.org.uk/cyberliber/59350/0038/005/0500.htm |doi=10.2307/3754991 |access-date=2018-10-19 |archive-date=2020-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200420120800/http://www.cybertruffle.org.uk/cyberliber/59350/0038/005/0500.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其下包含18個[[屬_(生物)|屬]]，共約1300種<ref name="Kirk 2008">{{cite book |vauthors=Kirk PM, Cannon PF, Minter DW, Stalpers JA |title=Dictionary of the Fungi |url=https://archive.org/details/dictionaryfungit00kirk |edition=10th |publisher=CAB International |location=Wallingford, UK |year=2008 |page=[https://archive.org/details/dictionaryfungit00kirk/page/671 671] |isbn=978-0-85199-826-8}}</ref>。本科物種的一項特徵是[[蕈傘|蕈傘]]上具有[[菌蓋皮|菌蓋皮]]，另外[[孢子印|孢子印]]多呈紅棕色至深棕色，[[擔孢子|擔孢子]]表面平滑且頂端有萌發孔，營養方式均為[[腐生|腐生]]。

